import React from 'react';
import { Box, Grid, Typography } from '@mui/material';

export const PresentationPage = () => {
   return (
      <Box sx={{ backgroundColor: "rgba(0, 145, 136, 0.8)" }}>
         <Grid container direction="column">
            <Grid item>
               <Typography sx={{ fontFamily: "Noto Sans", fontWeight: 400, fontSize: "20px" }}>
                  Olá! Eu sou Bianca Sakaniwa, uma
               </Typography>
            </Grid>
            <Grid item>
               <Typography>
                  Desenvolvedora de Software Fullstack
               </Typography>
            </Grid>
            <Grid item>
               <Typography>
                  Com ênfase em front-end
               </Typography>
            </Grid>
         </Grid>
      </Box>
   )
}
